The Services proposed several amendments to 脗搂芒聙聣402.14. Consistent with the Services' existing practice, we proposed to revise 脗搂芒聙聣402.14(c) to clarify what is necessary to initiate formal consultation and to allow the Services to consider documents such as those prepared pursuant to the National Environmental Policy Act (NEPA; 42 U.S.C. 4321 
